title: The 10 best photos of Melbourne's New Year's Eve fireworks
text:
By Rose Johnstone Posted: Sunday January 1 2017, 3:18pm Photograph: Wolf Cocklin 
Last night, half a million Melburnians and tourists gathered in the CBD to feast their eyes on the city's $500,000 New Year's Eve fireworks display. Sure, we might not have Sydney's world-famous Harbour Bridge pyrotechnics spectacular ‚Äì but we still know how to go out with a bang. 
If you missed out on seeing them this year, then check out these shots, all taken right at the perfect moment.
